OL,4,Cabuse and harrassment, major report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FWords by Political Correspondent
OL,8,FShehab Khan and Politics Producer Maya
OL,9,FBowles
OL,11,FMore than half the candidates in the
OL,12,FJuly General Election faced
OL,13,Fharassment, intimidation, or abuse,
OL,14,Faccording to a major report by the
OL,15,Felections watchdog.
OL,17,FThe findings from the Electoral
OL,18,FCommission reveal a concerning level
OL,19,Fof hostility directed at those running
OL,20,Ffor office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
