OL,3,COver half of election candidates faced
OL,4,Cabuse and harrassment, major report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FReacting to the report, the
OL,8,Fgovernment's advisor on political
OL,9,Fviolence, Lord Walney, told ITV News
OL,10,Fthat without more government action to
OL,11,Ftackle threats against candidates and
OL,12,FMPs, "we risk repeats of the kind of
OL,13,Fviolent attacks which have seen
OL,14,Ffrontline politicians be murdered".
OL,16,FThe review revealed 55% of candidates
OL,17,Fencountered some form of abuse or
OL,18,Fintimidation, while 56% opted to avoid
OL,19,Fcertain campaign activities out of
OL,20,Ffear for their safety.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
