OL,7,FChief Executive of the Electoral
OL,8,FCommission Vijay Rangarajan said the
OL,9,Flevel of harassment and intimidation
OL,10,Ffaced by candidates was "concerning"
OL,11,Fand requires "urgent and coordinated
OL,12,Faction."
OL,14,FHe warned the abuse is "deterring some
OL,15,Fpeople from standing to be candidates,
OL,16,Fand inhibiting how some engage with
OL,17,Fvoters".
