OL,7,FPreet Gill, the Labour MP for
OL,8,FBirmingham Edgbaston, said she's no
OL,9,Fstranger to abuse, but that this
OL,10,Felection was unprecedented in terms of
OL,11,Fthe harassment she faced.
OL,13,FDuring the campaign she had to report
OL,14,Fincidents to the police four times,
OL,15,Fafter she was verbally harassed while
OL,16,Fout with her daughter, had her
OL,17,Fcampaign placards targeted by vandals,
OL,18,Fand received abuse and death threats
OL,19,Fon social media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
