OL,7,F"It's not fair game that MPs should
OL,8,Fput up with this... I want to be able
OL,9,Fto walk about freely like everybody
OL,10,Felse", she told ITV News.
OL,12,FShe revealed her teenage children have
OL,13,Fbecome aware of the kind of daily
OL,14,Fthreats she faces, adding: "They
OL,15,Flegitimately ask me, 'Is someone going
OL,16,Fto kill you?'"
OL,18,F"When my daughter said that to me, I
OL,19,Fjust burst into tears."
