OL,7,FMany of the threats Gill faced during
OL,8,Fthis election were from people unhappy
OL,9,Fwith Labour's response to the war in
OL,10,FGaza. The words "murderer" and "blood
OL,11,Fon hands" were written on her campaign
OL,12,Fposters.
OL,14,FDiscussions about the safety of MPs'
OL,15,Fhave escalated since the October 7
OL,16,FHamas attacks in 2023 and the Israeli
OL,17,Fmilitary campaign in Gaza - with
OL,18,Fheightened tensions about the conflict
OL,19,Fspilling into the campaign trail for
OL,20,Fmany candidates in the July election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
