OL,7,FThe Electoral Commission report
OL,8,Fhighlighted: "Ongoing international
OL,9,Ftensions in some cases led to an
OL,10,Fincrease in antisemitic and
OL,11,FIslamophobic abuse directed at
OL,12,Fcandidates."
